Membrane <span>Biology</span>
</h1>

<p>
Membrane biology lipidomics studies how lipid composition, membrane organization, lipid–protein interactions, and membrane remodeling regulate cellular structure, signaling, metabolism, and disease.
</p>

<div class="hero-image">
